		 BIRTHDAY PARADOX VALIDATOR 
		-----------------------------

What is it ?
------------

This is a code to prove that the Birthday Paradox is valid.

Usage -
-------

Input to the program is the number of people in the group for which the paradox has to be proved. 
			

Implementation -
----------------

Language Used - C

The code is divided into 3 modules:

1) Calculating the mathematical probability for the number of people
   -----Explaination is at line no. 205 in the code
		
2) Running trials, calculating individual probabilities and comparing them with the mathematical probability
   -----Random birthdays are assigned to the people and the total repetitions are checked

3) Print result when calculated probability equals mathematical probability
	